context.extraction_guidelines: Focus on extracting data from the main content area where individual product listings are displayed. Look for repeating container patterns such as .s-item within the .srp-results container. Extract each listing's title (.s-item__title), price (.s-item__price), and condition (.s-item__subtitle). Avoid extracting data from filter sidebars (.x-refine), price range selectors, category breadcrumbs, related searches, and sorting dropdown options.
